Dangerous war confabs against DPRK
 &nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, January 21 (KCNA) -- The U.S. and the South Korean authorities recently held the 30th "annual consultative meeting on security" and the 20th "military committee" meeting for a war against the north.&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Papers here today carry commentaries in this regard.
   Warmongers at home and abroad published a "joint statement", the keynote of which is filled with "strong warning to the north," and U.S. Secretary of Defence William Cohen threatened to "punish" the north with "all means, including nuclear weapons," the news analyst of Rodong Sinmun says, and goes on:   The "joint statement" and Cohen's remarks make it a fait accompli to unleash a war against the north. They are an open threat and blackmail and declaration of a nuclear war against the DPRK.&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The issues of "underground nuclear facility" and "missile development" the warmongers raised in the war confabs against the north aim to invent an excuse for  igniting a nuclear war according to the "operation plan 5027".
   Answering "punishment" with punishment, a total war with total war and an aggressive war with liberation war is the character and mode of counteraction pertaining to the DPRK.
   If  the U.S., their henchmen and followers dare unleash a war against the DPRK, the Korean people and revolutionary armed forces will never miss the opportunity to plunge the provokers into a sea of fire and to reduce them to ashes.&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Minju Joson says that if warmongers unleash a war against the DPRK, it will annihilate the aggressors in reliance upon the invincible might which it has cultivated for scores of years and achieve the historic cause of national reunification.

Joint New Year Editorial studied abroad
&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, January 21 (KCNA) -- The Joint New Year Editorial of Rodong Sinmun, Joson Inmingun and Chongnyon Jonwi of the DPRK has been studied and disseminated in Russia, Tunisia, Madagascar and Guinea.&nbsp;&nbsp;
   At a seminar held in Moscow on Jan. 16 a reporter and speakers referred to last year's successes and this year's task, saying that this year will be a year of fresh turn in advance towards the building of a powerful nation in the DPRK.
   They pointed out that the monolithic unity of the leader, party and masses in the DPRK with the Juche Idea as its guideline will be further strengthened and the second grand march of Chollima will be sped up this year.
   Meanwhile, seminars, lecture meetings and reading sessions on the Joint Editorial were held in different countries.&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The participants stressed that as General Secretary Kim Jong Il leads the Korean revolution and the Korean people have the solid independent national economy and strong self-reliant defence capabilities, the DPRK will exalt itself as a powerful nation without fail.
